headline.main: Poland Seeks to Generate Support for Challenger to Tusk
headline.print_headline: Poland Seeks to Generate Support for Challenger to Tusk

lead_paragraph: Poland's surprise counter-candidate to challenge incumbent Donald Tusk for the post of European Council head is "Poland's only candidate in the game," and diplomats are trying to generate support for him, Polish officials said Monday.
